\":\"Dog Parks Directory\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Wake Forest\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"College Town Roots\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"children\":\"Wake Forest Walks\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-chip-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"hero-chip\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-label\",\"children\":\"Dog Parks\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-value\",\"children\":\"1\"}],\"$undefined\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"hero-chip\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-label\",\"children\":\"Trail Miles\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"chip-value\",\"children\":\"50+\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Wake Forest is beautiful. From the historic district to the sprawling fields of Joyner Park, it offers a picturesque setting for dog owners.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-rich-description\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"Wake Forest, North Carolina, offers a blend of historic charm and expansive natural beauty that is hard to beat. The crown jewel for dog owners is \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.wakeforestnc.gov/parks-recreation-cultural-resources/parks-facilities/e-carroll-joyner-park\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"E. Carroll Joyner Park\"}],null,\". This 117-acre former farm has been transformed into a stunning public space with miles of paved trails winding through stone walls, pecan groves, and open meadows. It is a photographer’s dream and a dog walker’s paradise, offering plenty of space to spread out and enjoy the outdoors knowing your dog is welcome on a leash.\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"rich-description-paragraph\",\"children\":[\"For off-leash socialization, Flaherty Dog Park provides the necessary amenities, including shaded areas and water fountains, ensuring a comfortable play session. Wake Forest is also a gateway to the Neuse River Greenway and Falls Lake, providing access to endless miles of trails for those seeking a longer adventure. The downtown area, with its historic architecture and vibrant street life (\\\"Friday Night on White\\\"), is increasingly dog-friendly, making Wake Forest a \",[\"$\",\"$L11\",\"1\",{\"href\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"rich-link\",\"children\":\"well-rounded community\"}],null,\" for pets and their people.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",\"Flaherty Dog Park\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Flaherty Dog Park\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Joyner Park\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Joyner Park\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Falls Lake Dam\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Falls Lake Dam\"]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-card\",\"children\":[\"$L12\",\"$L13\"]}]}]]}]}],\"$L14